analysis of canabalt scores. I'm constantly collecting data posted to twitter and will update the repository as appropriate.

I'm trying to determine a few things:

Does the device that canabalt is being played on influence the score? I.e. do iPad players score higher than iPod Touch players?

Do the best players tend to die by a certain method?

